summary: This cable discusses the potential exfiltration of AMFAUNA-25 from Cuba, in light of recent developments involving other AMFAUNA assets and the potential arrest of ANCUTLER-2. It proposes a plan to arrange a legal departure for AMFAUNA-25 under the guise of discussing Cuban insurance problems in London, involving Peter Minet of Minet Co London. The cable emphasizes the need for speed and coordination with SMOTH (likely a code name for an organization or individual) to ensure the success of the operation.
title: Exfiltration of AMFAUNA-25 from Cuba
